_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-297x210.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-800x567.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-120x85.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-768x544.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-696x493.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-1068x757.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-593x420.jpg 593w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134535/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_hub-erendering-inside-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>Inside, the Gravaa KAPS hub mechanism are both a mechanical orbital pump that generates air pressure and an electronic controller to engage/disengage the pump, each powered solely by rider pedal power.</p><p><a h