ys. Standard Shimano HG, MicroSpline, SRAM XD &amp; XD-R bodies will also be available. There will also be a range of thru-axle sizes, and both standard and Boost hub spacing.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets.jpg\" alt=\"Gravaa KAPS lightweight on-the-fly tire pressure adjustment, wireless TPMS, XC or gravel\" width=\"2000\" height=\"600\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets-297x89.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets-800x240.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets-120x36.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets-768x230.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09134351/Gravaa-KAPS-lightweight-on-the-fly-tire-pressure-adjustment_wireless-TPMS_wheelsets-1536x461.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.biker